{"word":"G5447 - φυσικῶς - physikōs - foo-see-koce' - Naturally","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φυσικῶς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">physikōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">foo-see-koce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Naturally</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சுபாவப்படி - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"in a natural manner, by nature, under the guidance of nature"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb frm <a href=\"#/G5446 - φυσικός - physikós - foo-see-kos'/5446\">G5446</a>; &ldquo;physically&rdquo;, that is, (by implication) <i>instinctively:</i> - naturally.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5446/5446\">G5446</a>, <a href=\"#/G5447/5447\">G5447</a>, <a href=\"#/G5449/5449\">G5449</a>"}]}